snippet.title: Magocracy: Experimentation Trailer #01
snippet.description:
The first trailer for my new game Magocracy: Experimentation. This shows off a 9v9 with the player using a normal shot with weather type thunderstorm.

Please visit my website: https://magocracyexperimentation.com/ for more details.
